  <h2>Class Schedule</h2>
  <p>Here is our weekly class schedule. We focus on practical martial arts training through three specialized sessions each week.</p>

  <ul>
    <li><span class="day-label">Monday</span><br>
      <strong>Striking Class</strong> (Karate, Hapkido, Shorinji Kempo) – 6:00 PM
